# 1. Introduction

The Budget Tracker with Savings Monitor is a simple Python-based application designed to help students monitor their expenses, manage their allowance, and track their savings goals. Many students struggle with budgeting, especially those living in dormitories or managing limited allowances. This program aims to provide a simple and beginner-friendly solution for tracking daily expenses and encouraging responsible financial habits.

